Soal 1: Multiple Subplots

Dengan data di bawah ini buatlah visualisasi seperti expected output:

x = np.linspace(2*-np.pi, 2*np.pi, 200)
tan = np.tan(x)/10
cos = np.cos(x)
sin = np.sin(x)

# code here
fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(20,8), nrows=1, ncols=3, sharey=True)
ax[0].plot(x, tan, color='b', label='tanX')
ax[0].set_title('Grafik tanX')
ax[1].plot(x, sin, color='r', label='sinX')
ax[1].set_title('Grafik sinX')
ax[2].plot(x, cos, color='g', label='cosX')
ax[2].set_title('Grafik cosX')

fig.legend(loc='upper center')
plt.show()

Soal 2: Nested Axis

Dengan data di bawah ini, buatlah visualisasi seperti expected output:

x = np.linspace(2*-np.pi, 2*np.pi, 100)
y = np.cos(x)
y2 = np.cos(x**2)
y3 = np.cos(x**3)
y4 = np.cos(x**4)
y5 = np.cos(x**5)

# code here
fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(12,7))
ax.plot(x, y)
ax.set_title('Grafik CosX')

ins4 = ax.inset_axes([0.9, 0.9, 0.32, 0.3])
ins4.set_title('Grafik CosX^4')
ins4.plot(x, y4, color='black')
ins4.plot(x, y, color='blue')

ins5 = ax.inset_axes([-0.1, 0.9, 0.32, 0.3])
ins5.set_title('Grafik CosX^5')
ins5.plot(x, y5, color='yellow')
ins5.plot(x, y, color='blue')

ins2 = ax.inset_axes([0.9, -0.1, 0.32, 0.3])
ins2.set_title('Grafik CosX^3')
ins2.plot(x, y3, color='green')
ins2.plot(x, y, color='blue')

ins3 = ax.inset_axes([-0.1, -0.1, 0.32, 0.3])
ins3.set_title('Grafik CosX^2')
ins3.plot(x, y2, color='red')
ins3.plot(x, y, color='blue')
